          <title>After delay, Trump signs agreement with Biden White House to begin formal transition handoff</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WASHINGTON (AP) — President-elect Donald Trump on Tuesday reached a required agreement with President Joe Biden’s White House to allow his transition staff to coordinate with the existing federal workforce before taking office on Jan. 20.]]></description>
